name: Let's Farty
description: We believe laughter is the best remedy, and our mission is to spread joy and break taboos about digestive health with humor and fun activities. In FartyLand, you can: Play the Farty Game: Time your "toots" with passing cars, earn Farty Points, and exchange them for rewards. Share Your Farts: Upload your best moments (like Tiktok videos) in our Telegram Mini-app, where users can vote to reward the top "toots". Ask Farty: Get tips and guidance from Farty, your Digestive Health AI Agent, covering gas, digestion, and healthy living. Every toot in FartyLand spreads laughter, rewards creativity, and promotes healthier living. Let's Farty!
